description:
As a merchant
  add to cart checkout prodcut set to fast checkeout
  check cart items (A + B + C) when child product sold out, A and C can't buy on fast checkout page
name: Fast-Checkout - prodcut set child product sold out check error message

elements.name: Fast-Checkout prodcut set child product(B) sold out check error message - cart itme(C)

steps.name: I am on Admin Login Page
I fill correct account email to email field
I fill correct account password to password field
I click on login button
I should see successful login
I check intercom message notification frame and click clear intercom message button
I check intercom message notification frame and click intercom message close button
I check new feature alert notification frame and click new feature alert close button
I check and click exclude products panel close button
I check and click no thanks button
I am on Shop Product Index Layout V Two Page
I hover over search icon
I input "PDP sold out product set" to search field
1st product of products list should contain 'PDP sold out product set'

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"(dirty data) PDP sold out product setUS$160.00US$200.00","expectText":"PDP sold out product set"}

steps.name: I click on 1st product of products list
I should be redirected to Shop Product Show Layout V Two Page
I click on add to cart button
I click on checkout button
I should be redirected to Shop Fast Checkout Page
I switch to 2 of tabs
I am on Inventory Page
I input "9th Product for Checkout" to search field
I should see row of product list
1st row of product list should contain '9th Product for Checkout'

embeddings.data: {"elementText":"9th Product for Checkout Published OFF 8902221Blue, S 2222Add SetSaveBlue, M 1899999Add SetSaveRed, S 3000000Add SetSaveRed, M 4000000Add SetSave","expectText":"9th Product for Checkout"}

steps.name: I fill "0" to 1st row of quantity field
I click on set button
I click on 1st save button
I switch to 1 of tabs
I should be redirected to Shop Fast Checkout Page
I click on delivery option included 'Local Delivery'
I click on payment option included 'Custom'

embeddings.data: {"retryCount":1,"elementTexts":["","Credit Card via Stripe","Credit Card via Stripe","","Custom","Cash on Delivery","Bank Transfer"],"text":"Custom"}

steps.name: I select recipient address dropdown option included 'United States' of recipient address dropdown
I wait for 5 seconds for loading
I select recipient address dropdown option included "New York" of 2nd recipient address dropdown
I fill name to customer name field
I fill email to customer email field
I click on become member checkbox
I click on accept marketing checkbox
I fill name to recipient name field
I fill '81234567' to recipient phone field
I fill address to recipient address field
I fill city to 2nd recipient address field
I fill city to recipient city field
I fill '10001' to recipient post code field
I scroll down to place order button
I click on place order button
I should see error alert
error alert should contain 'There is at least one unavailable product in the shopping cart. Please adjust the cart items to checkout, or try to refresh page.'

I should be redirected to Shop Fast Checkout Page
I should see 1 remove hyperlink
